		<!-- Introduction Section -->
		<div class="section-1">
			<div class="rectangle-1-shadow"></div>
			<div class="rectangle-1">
				<h1>About Us</h1>
				<p>
					At Task App, we help you plan and organize your day, week,
					month, and year with a fast, simple, and effective task
					planner. Join us for a free one-week trial and discover how
					easy it is to stay on top of your goals.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!-- How It Works Section -->
		<div class="section-2">
			<div class="rectangle-2"></div>
			<div class="rectangle-3">
				<h1>This is Task App</h1>
				<div class="short-line"></div>
				<p class="sentence-1">You create your tasks with ease</p>
				<p>
					Staying productive requires the right tools. A task creation
					app simplifies the process of organizing daily
					responsibilities, setting deadlines, and tracking progress.
				</p>
				<p>
					With an intuitive interface, users can quickly add tasks,
					categorize them, and prioritize what matters most. Reminders
					ensure that important deadlines are never missed, while
					recurring task options help with routine planning.
				</p>
				<p>
					Collaboration features allow teams to work together
					seamlessly, assigning tasks and sharing updates in real
					time. Whether managing personal goals or professional
					projects, a structured task system keeps everything in
					order.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!-- Founder Introduction -->
		<div class="section-3">
			<div class="rectangle-4">
				<blockquote class="whole-sentence">
					<span class="double-quotes">
						<span class="first-sentence"
							>Task App began with a simple thought - How</span
